		<item>
		<title>Project Highlight: Zac Poissant, UX Design</title>
		<link>https://brainstation.io/blog/project-highlight-zac-poissant-ux-design</link>
				<pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2020 21:00:55 +0000</pubDate>
